    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "letting go sounds nice in theory, but how do you actually do that when everyone looks at you like you're nothing? it feels like the social death is already done. there's no coming back from this kind of disgrace. once you've lost everything that made you \"you\", what's even the point of staying in the game?",
